headline: ASE and Analog Devices Announce Strategic Collaboration
summary: PENANG, Malaysia & WILMINGTON, Mass., October 21, 2025--ASE Technology Holding Co., Ltd. (NYSE: ASX, TAIEX: 3711), and Analog Devices, Inc. (NASDAQ: ADI), today announced strategic joint efforts in Penang, Malaysia with the signing of a binding Memorandum of Understanding.
